OL,3,CWarning over 'catastrophic levels' of
OL,4,Cdrugs, violence and rats in prison
OL,6,FA prison with "catastrophic levels" of
OL,7,Fdrugs, organised crime, high rates of
OL,8,Fviolence and a rat infestation is in
OL,9,Furgent need of improvement, an
OL,10,Finspection has found.
OL,12,FHMP Manchester, previously known as
OL,13,FStrangeways, was found by HM
OL,14,FInspectorate of Prisons to be the most
OL,15,Fviolent of all adult men's prisons in
OL,16,FEngland and Wales, with the highest
OL,17,Frate of serious assaults.
