OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F396A1728584601
OL,3,CWarning over 'catastrophic levels' of
OL,4,Cdrugs, violence and rats in prison
OL,6,F"The prison service must act urgently
OL,7,Fto address this and to support staff
OL,8,Fto manage a very challenging
OL,9,Fpopulation of prisoners.
OL,11,F"But Manchester is not alone in facing
OL,12,Fthese challenges which are becoming
OL,13,Fendemic in many parts of the prison
OL,14,Festate and demand the attention of the
OL,15,FGovernment."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
