OL,3,CWarning over 'catastrophic levels' of
OL,4,Cdrugs, violence and rats in prison
OL,6,FIn an urgent notification letter sent
OL,7,Fto Justice Secretary Shabana Mahmood,
OL,8,FMr Taylor said the number of weapons
OL,9,Fand illicit items found in the prison
OL,10,Fin recent months was among the highest
OL,11,Fof all adult men's prisons.
OL,13,FIt added that 39% of prisoners had
OL,14,Ftested positive for drug use in the
OL,15,Flast 12 months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
