OL,3,CWarning over 'catastrophic levels' of
OL,4,Cdrugs, violence and rats in prison
OL,6,FMore than half of inmates said they
OL,7,Fhad felt unsafe at some point and
OL,8,Fthere had been six self-inflicted
OL,9,Fdeaths and three deaths with suspected
OL,10,Flinks to drug abuse since the last
OL,11,Finspection, the letter said.
OL,13,FInspectors found the prison was
OL,14,F"filthy", with a chronic rodent
OL,15,Finfestation, and many cell windows
OL,16,Fwere smashed, prompting prisoners to
OL,17,Fuse foam from mattresses and pillows
OL,18,Fto push into window frames to stop the
OL,19,Fcold getting in.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
