OL,3,CWarning over 'catastrophic levels' of
OL,4,Cdrugs, violence and rats in prison
OL,6,FPrisons minister Lord Timpson said an
OL,7,Faction plan to deliver urgent
OL,8,Fimprovements would be published in the
OL,9,Fcoming weeks.
OL,11,FHe said: "Reports such as this have
OL,12,Fbecome far too common. They typify the
OL,13,Fshocking state of the prison system we
OL,14,Fhave inherited.
OL,16,F"Every day our dedicated staff do
OL,17,Fvital work keeping the public safe.
OL,18,FThey deserve better than being faced
OL,19,Fwith conditions such as these and the
OL,20,Fconstant threat of violence.
