OL,3,CWarning over 'catastrophic levels' of
OL,4,Cdrugs, violence and rats in prison
OL,6,F"That is why this Government took
OL,7,Fimmediate action to end the
OL,8,Fovercrowding crisis engulfing our
OL,9,Fjails. We will now continue the hard
OL,10,Fwork to ensure prisons like HMP
OL,11,FManchester become places that create
OL,12,Fbetter citizens and not better
OL,13,Fcriminals.
OL,15,F"The Governor and his team continue to
OL,16,Fdo a great job in very difficult
OL,17,Fcircumstances and are already working
OL,18,Fto address the inspectors' concerns."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUzD@eO]
