OL,3,CWarning over 'catastrophic levels' of
OL,4,Cdrugs, violence and rats in prison
OL,6,FHMP Manchester, which houses category
OL,7,FA and B prisoners, was the scene of
OL,8,Fthe longest prison riot in British
OL,9,Fhistory, lasting from April 1 to April
OL,10,F25 1990.
OL,12,FAndrew Neilson, director of campaigns
OL,13,Fat the Howard League for Penal Reform,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Drugs are a scourge in prison,
OL,15,Fleading to debt and ultimately
OL,16,Fviolence and self-harm.
OL,18,F"Security at Manchester prison must be
OL,19,Ftightened, clearly, but ultimately the
OL,20,Fway to combat drugs is to reduce
OL,21,Fdemand for them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
