OL,3,CWarning over 'catastrophic levels' of
OL,4,Cdrugs, violence and rats in prison
OL,6,F"This means ensuring well-trained
OL,7,Fstaff get men out of their cells and
OL,8,Finto activities that will help them to
OL,9,Flive healthily and move on from crime.
OL,11,F"This is the scale of the challenge
OL,12,Fconfronting the new Government.
OL,13,FInstead of wasting resources on
OL,14,Fbuilding new jails, we should focus on
OL,15,Frestoring order and decency to the
OL,16,Fones we already have."
